These non-standard libraries are required to address the cameras and the
steering servo. The libraries can obtained from:

libPvAPI:   Prosilica's download page
libiowkit:  Code Mercenaries download page. The library is generated from
            the file iowkit.c which you can find in the libiowkit subproject

subdirectory lib/ contains the 32-bit versions, lib64/ the 64-bit versions
